[
    {
        "start": 0.0,
        "end": 3.48,
        "text": "I've had probably two extremely dark phases in my life",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 3.48,
        "end": 5.34,
        "text": "and in both those phases my first instinct was",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 5.34,
        "end": 7.46,
        "text": "go home, sit alone and listen to Kunfaya Kun.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 7.52,
        "end": 9.3,
        "text": "It's helped so many people.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 9.4,
        "end": 11.2,
        "text": "If you take all the truths in the world",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 11.2,
        "end": 13.68,
        "text": "as a Sufi I believe that it all comes from the same source.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 14.0,
        "end": 14.62,
        "text": "Like Rumi says,",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 14.8,
        "end": 17.0,
        "text": "there's a place beyond good things and bad things, I'll see you there.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 17.12,
        "end": 18.42,
        "text": "The Kunfaya Kun comes from the holy book",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 18.42,
        "end": 20.3,
        "text": "and it says how God created the world.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 20.42,
        "end": 22.72,
        "text": "So when Tiaz Ali and Noe said that",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 22.72,
        "end": 24.04,
        "text": "can we use this as a Qawwali, I said,",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 24.1,
        "end": 25.76,
        "text": "I got shaken, I was like, what are you trying to do?",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": true
    },
    {
        "start": 25.88,
        "end": 27.2,
        "text": "You know, destroy me, you know what?",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": true
    },
    {
        "start": 27.2,
        "end": 30.1,
        "text": "Because it's the most sacred word from the holy book.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 30.38,
        "end": 32.34,
        "text": "Many faiths are all interconnected with commonality.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 32.48,
        "end": 33.76,
        "text": "Commonality is about empathy.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 33.94,
        "end": 35.96,
        "text": "Commonality is about glorifying the creator.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 36.16,
        "end": 36.92,
        "text": "They call him different names.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 37.1,
        "end": 39.42,
        "text": "Somebody from the West who don't understand a word of it",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 39.42,
        "end": 40.36,
        "text": "is responding to it.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 40.46,
        "end": 41.64,
        "text": "And from India, every faith,",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 41.86,
        "end": 43.1,
        "text": "Muslims, Christians or Hindus,",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 43.22,
        "end": 44.26,
        "text": "and this is beyond politics.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 44.44,
        "end": 46.82,
        "text": "This is the true core of spirituality,",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 46.82,
        "end": 48.52,
        "text": "transferring from an audio.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    }
]